## A. LEARNING PHILOSOPHY (STABLE)

- Depth > speed
    
- Problem-first, tool-second
    
- Red + Blue together
    
- Labs > theory
    
- Build identity, not flex
    
- Documentation is for clarity, not ego
    
- Learn topics to **remove mystery**, not to collect tools
    

