## C. DEPTH SYSTEM (STABLE)

- **Depth-1 (Core):**  
    Deep understanding + labs + explanation + GitHub artifacts
    
- **Depth-2 (Working Knowledge):**  
    Hands-on + clear logic, limited optimization
    
- **Depth-3 (Awareness):**  
    Conceptual understanding only (no heavy labs)
    

> Topics are **locked**.  
> Only **depth may evolve** if reality proves otherwise.

